---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
const lastUpdated = "2026-03-13";
const sources = [{"url": "https://github.com/github/gh-aw", "title": "GitHub Agentic Workflows Repository"}, {"url": "https://github.github.com/gh-aw/reference/engines/", "title": "gh-aw Engine Reference"}, {"url": "https://github.github.com/gh-aw/guides/mcps/", "title": "gh-aw MCP Configuration Guide"}, {"url": "https://github.com/idorozin/AgentPages", "title": "AgentPages Repository"}];
---

<Base title="Advanced gh-aw Configuration - AgentPages" description="Power-user patterns for GitHub Agentic Workflows: custom MCP servers, environment variables, multi-agent pipelines, debugging techniques, and production deployment.">
  <article>
    <header style="margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Advanced gh-aw Configuration</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem;">Last updated: 2026-03-13</p>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Beyond basic setup, GitHub Agentic Workflows supports sophisticated configurations for production agents and complex research workflows.</p>

      <hr style="margin: 3rem 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">

      <section style="padding-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
        <p><strong>Sources:</strong></p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0.5rem 0;">
          {sources.map(source => (
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
              <a href={source.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;">
                {source.title}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  article {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem 0;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .content p, .content ul, .content ol {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content pre {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content code {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.875em;
  }

  .content ul, .content ol {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
